01:05.165 --> 01:06.365
Oh! Down, boy.

01:06.399 --> 01:08.468
Can I do "aerob-tics" with you?

01:08.501 --> 01:10.970
Uh, no. Go find a friend to play with.

01:11.004 --> 01:14.308
Hmm. Where, oh,
where can I find a friend?

01:14.340 --> 01:15.575
A friend!

01:15.608 --> 01:17.210
Friend, friend, friend!

01:17.243 --> 01:20.046
Where can I find a friend?

01:21.013 --> 01:22.949
Hey, quit hogging the ball.

01:22.983 --> 01:24.084
I want to put it in!

01:24.117 --> 01:26.286
Not before I shoot it
all over your face!

01:26.319 --> 01:28.822
Hi! Can I play with you guys?

01:28.855 --> 01:30.757
No. You have leg braces.

01:30.790 --> 01:31.792
Huh?

01:31.825 --> 01:33.460
Yeah, loser!

01:33.492 --> 01:35.328
Oh! Aah!

01:35.361 --> 01:36.562
Aaaah!

01:36.596 --> 01:38.564
Aw, no!

01:38.597 --> 01:40.667
My leg braces "breaked."

01:41.085 --> 01:44.070
Identify yourself!

01:44.103 --> 01:46.507
Huh? Who said that?

01:47.301 --> 01:49.343
I repeat, identify yourself.

01:49.742 --> 01:50.978
I'm Tommy.

01:51.010 --> 01:52.912
Target identified.

01:52.945 --> 01:53.914
Who are you?!

01:53.947 --> 01:55.582
I am S.H.O.E.S., which stands for

01:55.614 --> 01:58.317
Secret Hyper Operational
Exoskeleton System.

01:58.350 --> 02:00.420
What does "Tommy" stand for?

02:00.453 --> 02:02.256
Nothing. I can't stand.

02:02.289 --> 02:03.590
Whoa!

02:03.623 --> 02:06.026
See, I was looking for a friend but...

02:06.058 --> 02:08.693
What is "friend"?

02:08.728 --> 02:12.533
Oh. A friend is somebody
you do things with.

02:12.566 --> 02:15.435
Could I be friend?

02:15.467 --> 02:17.637
Whee!

02:17.670 --> 02:20.473
Whoa! That's so fast!

02:20.507 --> 02:22.709
- Whoa!
- Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa,

02:22.741 --> 02:24.644
whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa! Ha!

02:24.677 --> 02:25.811
- Amazing!
- Amazing!

02:25.844 --> 02:27.713
You ain't seen nothing yet!

02:27.747 --> 02:33.020
Ha! Who-o-o-o-o-o-a!

02:33.052 --> 02:34.054
Ow!

02:35.155 --> 02:35.989
You suck!

02:36.021 --> 02:37.223
But those shoes are awesome!

02:37.257 --> 02:38.391
- Huh?
- Grab him!

02:38.425 --> 02:39.993
Yeah, let's tug 'em off!

02:40.026 --> 02:41.395
Aah! No!

02:41.427 --> 02:42.728
Target identified!

02:42.762 --> 02:43.729
Cool!

02:43.763 --> 02:44.865
Destroy target.

02:44.897 --> 02:46.400
No! Come on, S.H.O.E.S.

02:46.432 --> 02:47.633
Let's get out of here.

02:47.667 --> 02:49.368
Affirmative. Getting out of here.

02:49.401 --> 02:50.536
Whoa!

02:50.569 --> 02:51.737
Hey! Come back with those shoes!

02:51.770 --> 02:54.591
Sir, I've got eyes on S.H.O.E.S.

02:55.108 --> 02:57.978
No, I am not paying a $3 late fee.

02:58.010 --> 03:00.343
Dad, meet my friend S.H.O.E.S.

03:00.475 --> 03:04.016
Well, I'd like to see you try
and take $3 from me, buddy.

03:04.050 --> 03:05.686
Hand it over!

03:05.718 --> 03:07.587
What? No. You'll never get it from me.

03:07.621 --> 03:09.323
Oh, I see.

03:09.355 --> 03:12.158
Well, I better go get my gun,
and we'll settle this like men.

03:12.192 --> 03:14.260
Tommy, they found me. It's over.

03:14.294 --> 03:17.097
Listen, kid. S.H.O.E.S. was
designed for the military,

03:17.129 --> 03:19.765
but some pairs began
developing a mind of their own

03:19.799 --> 03:21.401
and learned how to tie their own laces.

03:21.433 --> 03:24.437
We need to destroy S.H.O.E.S.
before someone gets hurt!

03:24.471 --> 03:26.173
But he's my friend!

03:26.205 --> 03:28.841
No! He's a cold-blooded killing machine!

03:28.875 --> 03:30.743
Yep. He's evil all right.

03:30.776 --> 03:32.411
- Huh?
- Oh, no! They got away!

03:32.444 --> 03:33.680
What? No! Damn it!

03:33.712 --> 03:35.448
He has an underground
lair with prisoners

03:35.481 --> 03:37.010
and a river of blood.

03:37.155 --> 03:39.886
Hmm. This is worse than we thought.
Move out.

03:39.919 --> 03:41.588
We're gonna have to get more creative

03:41.621 --> 03:42.789
to get him away from the kid.

03:42.822 --> 03:44.358
What's all this commotion?

03:44.390 --> 03:46.025
Looks like I'm not the only one

03:46.058 --> 03:48.021
that knows Mr. Pickles is evil.

03:48.126 --> 03:49.263
Ugh. Never mind.

03:49.295 --> 03:53.466
Now, I got two BBs that says
you won't take $3 from me!

03:53.500 --> 03:55.468
You cowards! Get out of here!

03:55.502 --> 03:57.204
Whoa!

03:57.236 --> 03:59.472
S.H.O.E.S.,
we need to find a safe place.

03:59.506 --> 04:02.141
- Okay. In here.
- Huh?

04:02.175 --> 04:04.478
Aah! Tommy, I'm in the bath!

04:04.510 --> 04:06.280
Aaaaaaaah!

04:07.813 --> 04:11.150
- Hold on, Tommy.
- Oh! Whoa!

04:11.183 --> 04:13.486
Ooh, ooh! Oh! Not now, Tommy!

04:13.520 --> 04:14.655
I'm in the middle of something!

04:14.687 --> 04:17.257
Aaaaaaaaaaaaah!

04:18.824 --> 04:21.894
Oh! Here's A Safe Place.

04:21.927 --> 04:23.663
- Huh?
- Hi.

04:23.697 --> 04:24.831
- Cut!
- Huh?

04:24.863 --> 04:26.666
What are you doing on set?

04:26.699 --> 04:28.301
Are we safe?

04:28.334 --> 04:29.871
Say that again.

04:29.977 --> 04:31.404
Are we safe?

04:31.613 --> 04:33.339
You're Safe all right!

04:33.372 --> 04:38.644
The role of Johnny Safe will
now be played by these shoes.

04:38.677 --> 04:39.680
What?!

04:39.713 --> 04:41.515
Uh-huh!

04:43.115 --> 04:46.185
♪ Tony Safe was a
major-league umpire ♪

04:46.218 --> 04:49.322
♪ Then his wife died in
a major-league fire ♪

04:49.355 --> 04:52.677
♪ He can call a strike,
he can call a ball ♪

04:52.782 --> 04:56.226
♪ He's got five kids,
can he raise them all? ♪

04:56.529 --> 04:59.332
♪ When it feels like
you're all alone ♪

04:59.365 --> 05:02.134
♪ Always know there's
a place called home ♪

05:02.168 --> 05:08.175
♪ 'Cause ho-o-o-me's a safe place ♪

05:08.208 --> 05:09.343
Safe!

05:12.911 --> 05:15.715
Hey, Dad, can I borrow the car tonight?

05:15.749 --> 05:18.185
I have a date with Denise DeCarlo.

05:18.218 --> 05:19.653
She is one hot babe.

05:19.685 --> 05:20.986
Va-va-va-va-voom!

05:21.019 --> 05:23.322
Hold it, lover boy.

05:23.355 --> 05:24.658
Did you make the team?

05:24.690 --> 05:27.083
- Uh...
- He made the team all right...

05:27.228 --> 05:28.728
the chess team.

05:28.762 --> 05:30.062
Chess?

05:30.096 --> 05:32.899
You want the car,
make the baseball team.

05:32.965 --> 05:37.793
Maybe then you'll get to first
base with Denise DeCarlo.

05:38.149 --> 05:40.006
But I don't like baseball.

05:40.038 --> 05:41.640
Well, as long as you're in my house,

05:41.673 --> 05:44.577
