05:44.610 --> 05:46.980
Outta here!

05:47.012 --> 05:50.483
Aw,
I wish you died in the fire and not Mom.

05:51.718 --> 05:52.753
- Cut!
- Huh?

05:52.786 --> 05:54.521
Oh! Go away, boy.

05:54.553 --> 05:56.222
I'm acting with my friend!

05:58.458 --> 05:59.926
Great work, S.H.O.E.S.!

05:59.959 --> 06:02.596
The network wants to make you the star.

06:02.864 --> 06:03.730
Star?

06:03.762 --> 06:05.364
Yeah, but one thing...

06:05.398 --> 06:06.600
