06:06.632 --> 06:08.033
Uh... S.H.O.E.S.?

06:08.067 --> 06:09.903
Sorry, Tommy. You're dragging me down.

06:09.935 --> 06:13.239
Detaching. I'm going to be a star!

06:13.273 --> 06:14.408
Ha! Wha...

06:14.440 --> 06:16.742
We've got S.H.O.E.S.!
Move out, move out!

06:16.776 --> 06:17.877
Let's get...

06:17.911 --> 06:19.278
Outta here!

06:20.779 --> 06:22.715
Stupid kid!

06:22.749 --> 06:24.384
Wait! No! Aah!

06:24.416 --> 06:27.286
S.H.O.E.S.!

06:28.420 --> 06:30.757
Hey, look! It's that stupid kid's dog!

06:30.790 --> 06:32.225
Loser!

06:33.560 --> 06:35.461
S.H.O.E.S.!

06:35.495 --> 06:37.297
